From: As Tsaqib <0xfiqks@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] profile: discovery: parse every command-line option

The loop called getopt() once in its condition and again at the bottom of
each iteration. The second call discarded every other option, so using both
SM-DS and IMEI could silently omit one of them.
---
 src/applet/profile/discovery.c | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

--- a/src/applet/profile/discovery.c
+++ b/src/applet/profile/discovery.c
@@ -42,7 +42,6 @@ static int applet_main(int argc, char **
             return -1;
             break;
         }
-        opt = getopt(argc, argv, opt_string);
     }
 
     if (smds == NULL) {
